    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028930/extras/286aa31d487162cb1f3b26e6a2fb0e62.avif?t=1762000921\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028930/extras_big/286aa31d487162cb1f3b26e6a2fb0e62.avif?t=1762000921 width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome</strong> to the arena! Are you strong enough for the FreakShow? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Well...<i>unfortunately</i> you do not have a choice, be the victor or die trying!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028930/extras/7efc1971ab7748502f84d551d8ee9afc.poster.avif?t=1762000921\" width=506 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028930/extras/7efc1971ab7748502f84d551d8ee9afc.webm?t=1762000921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028930/extras/7efc1971ab7748502f84d551d8ee9afc.mp4?t=1762000921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The FreakShow is a game show set in a post apocalyptic world.</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Team of 3 Players battles enemy team for glory and wealth</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smile! You are on camera... and the Jumbotron!!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Live Announcer!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You have to learn to be STRATEGIC in the arena:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Figure out the balance of managing your own zombie horde and fighting along side them!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place defenses to protect your own base from the enemy! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Work together as a team to DEMOLISH your opponents!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028930/extras/2c95c9ee39450091182b254cda7bffd3.poster.avif?t=1762000921\" width=506 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028930/extras/2c95c9ee39450091182b254cda7bffd3.webm?t=1762000921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028930/extras/2c95c9ee39450091182b254cda7bffd3.mp4?t=1762000921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <strong>Surviving in FreakShow is about more than just brute force; it requires strategy, stealth, and well timed attacks.</strong>   </p>",
